</div>

<table>
<tr><th>步骤</th><th>模块</th><th>在端/云</th><th>在后台做什么 → 生成 DSL</th></tr>
<tr><td>1</td><td><b>13-1</b></td><td>云·后台</td><td>场景名 = "【正式】-【情感】-上车打招呼"，优先级 = 5。<code>scene_name, priority: 5</code></td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td><b>13-2</b></td><td>云·后台</td><td>渠道 = 上汽 DNA，车型 = D6X 全部，软件版本 ≥ 3.2.0。<code>effective_scope: {channel: "saic_dna", model: "D6X", sw_version: ">=3.2.0"}</code></td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td><b>13-3</b></td><td>云·后台</td><td>本场景不涉及 VLM 视觉感知，跳过</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td><b>13-4</b></td><td>云·后台</td><td>静态条件：条件1 = 人物动作"上车"（位置任意）AND 条件2 = 座椅占位"有人"。<code>conditions: [{signal: "action", field: "上车", seat: "any"}, {signal: "seat_occupied", value: true, logic: "AND"}]</code></td></tr>
